{"tid":2261615,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"10人犯聚消夜食出禍  敬酒不飲扯女警髮 沙展認襲擊罪","createTime":"2020-10-28T12:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T00:17:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6932093e1e12078ff9841196ab999c87e17e3071","tid":2261615,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/NAV5IJAIK5HLJIS5FN4FSULD2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FNAV5IJAIK5HLJIS5FN4FSULD2M%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7MvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=cb8f399d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FNAV5IJAIK5HLJIS5FN4FSULD2M%2F&h=ded33461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/NAV5IJAIK5HLJIS5FN4FSULD2M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n10人犯聚消夜食出禍 <br />\n敬酒不飲扯女警髮 沙展認襲擊罪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】天水圍警署10名警員今年4月下班後違限聚令，一同食消夜為女同袍送行，怎料發生警長打女警事件。涉案警長一再提出守行為了事但失敗，昨在開審前改口認罪。庭上披露事緣女警向警長敬酒被拒，不但揶揄警長，紅酒更濺中他的白鞋，憤而扯女警頭髮十秒。辯方求情指警長會失去工作，遭裁判官水佳麗質疑「有冇咁嚴重」後改口稱很大機會失去工作。水官明言「唔係事實唔好隨便講」，不要信口開河。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：官斥10警飯聚公然違例<br />\n<br />\n現已停職的被告梁珏榮（40歲）於4月19日在元朗屏會街屏會中心外的行人路襲擊31歲女警蘇伶雅，水官先索閱被告背景及社會服務令報告，准被告保釋至下月10日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_gtu7gKIOj35B-LAMvbZqDBhnCw=/720x592/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V35EXJAG75HQ7C5DQZE7J7CQZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_gtu7gKIOj35B-LAMvbZqDBhnCw%3D%2F720x592%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV35EXJAG75HQ7C5DQZE7J7CQZQ.jpg&h=e2cce4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告梁珏榮昨在開審前改口認罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白鞋被酒濺中復遭揶揄<br />\n<br />\n被告與女警蘇伶雅及八名同袍事發當晚到元朗吃消夜歡送蘇，蘇多次向被告敬酒，均遭被告拒絕。蘇揶揄被告不能再喝，兩人因此爭執，同袍分開他們，並帶蘇離開，惟蘇行至屏會中心外時遭被告追上，被告扯蘇頭髮約10秒。被告跟。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方昨求情時一度稱女警向前仆，被告才扯女警頭髮。水佳麗問辯方：「想扯佢起身？所以扯頭髮？」控方表明不接受這說法，更向辯方稱「咁你唔好認罪」。辯方稍後收回有關「扯頭髮起身」一說。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指被告1998年當差，20年後晉升為警長，獲警隊內部、美國執法部門及市民讚賞廿次。被告性格並非暴戾，事後向心理醫。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IBdfzGOHiIWAAaZi7cVAV12oD-k=/1576x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LS5YO2YWSRCE7FUBU2XQTMDZ4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIBdfzGOHiIWAAaZi7cVAV12oD-k%3D%2F1576x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLS5YO2YWSRCE7FUBU2XQTMDZ4E.jpg&h=5ac72b9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■天水圍警署10名警員今年4月違反限聚令到元朗食消夜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官：行為不受控令人困惑<br />\n<br />\n水官指被告不願飲酒，值得稱許；兩人案發時均非當值，但法庭須保護執法人員，而被告並非一下撞開女警，而是追上前施襲，行為不受控，實令人困惑。水官期望被告。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC926/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Puw4wE5uXzPaPBXPrH-Gu2x9ti0=/1547x2222/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MIN3QD4GU5DE5J2LSLOKDV5XEY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPuw4wE5uXzPaPBXPrH-Gu2x9ti0%3D%2F1547x2222%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMIN3QD4GU5DE5J2LSLOKDV5XEY.gif&h=6bf46fcb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc34f4b6232e9d42215ca2d107d2b84627732265","tid":2261615,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6932093e1e12078ff9841196ab999c87e17e3071","tid":2261615,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/NAV5IJAIK5HLJIS5FN4FSULD2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FNAV5IJAIK5HLJIS5FN4FSULD2M%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7MvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=cb8f399d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledai